{"tid":2342790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「聖誕老人送大禮」比利時聖誕老人成超級播毒者 訪老人院傳染157人18死","createTime":"2020-12-27T11:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T12:06:28.000Z","uid":33359,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"212d1adfb6678d3b1871af865bf55a4172cdcd50","tid":2342790,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:46:23.000Z","msg":"美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）14日報導，比利時佛萊明大區（Flanders）莫爾市（Mol）一名男子日前打扮成聖誕老人造訪一間護理之家，結果疑似導致75人感染武漢肺炎、1人病歿。<br />\n<br />\n莫爾市政府表示，男子是其中一位居民的兒子，他在造訪護理之家後確診。當局說，男子「造訪護理之家時並未感到不適」，「該活動亦未受到危機中心的認可，否則將會要求男子提供篩檢陰性證明。」<br />\n<br />\n市府透過聲明指出，護理之家允許男子到訪是「判斷錯誤」。當局續指，需要「深入科學研究」以證明男子的到訪是否就是護理之家爆發群聚感染的原因。當局補充，目前已有61名居民、14名工作人員確診。其中一名接受安寧照護的居民病歿，另一名重症居民正接受氧氣治療，「大部份」患者狀況良好，沒有出現任何武肺症狀。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，「與媒體報導相反，聖誕老人並沒有探訪每個房間，（護理之家）管理階層向我們保證，聖誕老人只探訪了包括休息區在內的公共區域。他一直與居民保持距離，且在每個地方停留的時間只有幾分鐘，也沒有發送禮物。」<br />\n<br />\n和大部份歐洲鄰國一樣，比利時也爆發第二波疫情。10月底時醫療系統幾近崩潰，第三大城烈日甚至要求確診但沒有症狀的醫護人員繼續工作。<br />\n<br />\n根據約翰霍普金斯大學統計，比利時累計確診病例60萬8137例、1萬7951死。（盧宥竹／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2832098/danta0_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2832098%2Fdanta0_1024.jpg&h=0a52c5c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2adbdb901e4b410d8b7ed846f9fbfe72793ddda","tid":2342790,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"播毒師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14912e7cdceb71acec325b160f8e2a328d451113","tid":2342790,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:48:32.000Z","msg":"賀年送鳩猴"},{"pid":"565f17e44c24d765e71388aa480d1cb4b2b1ce83","tid":2342790,"uid":383632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"傳染師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546e08b5aa6912fc5b3720b55380305fe09cd523","tid":2342790,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3c08f46e5e47d03e816a2bde44a4bd3b249bde","tid":2342790,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"播毒師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8433c20ecfc91bc5378a2f992835df8b11ca2f1e","tid":2342790,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"老人院師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ec7e35b1dc5d0350e381ad21448c82f9642487","tid":2342790,"uid":343544,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:51:51.000Z","msg":"送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3357f693224e8a1e229ae0efc6b003dc1daaefd3","tid":2342790,"uid":284001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"牛頭馬面"},{"pid":"4893fc92469c02022f32580d0b2671f0472cf6ec","tid":2342790,"uid":318204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b8856374f69bb55f166f969b929da9f11ff081","tid":2342790,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"其實都好慘<br />\n如果冇支肺<br />\n大家都會平安度過聖誕&hellip;<br />\n可以見到屋企人"},{"pid":"8da9d583a5a368503388e15cb31a09f84f30ca47","tid":2342790,"uid":161222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020